- I know who I'm talking to.

487
00:35:40,007 --> 00:35:43,469
Tell Devlin if Vaughn isn't
on the other end of this earpiece

488
00:35:43,552 --> 00:35:46,889
when I turn it on,
the CIA gets nothing.

489
00:35:46,972 --> 00:35:49,975
Vaughn is a junior officer.

490
00:35:50,684 --> 00:35:52,853
Then promote him.

491
00:35:57,066 --> 00:36:00,778
Daniel's apartment was here.
The cameras were off here to here.

492
00:36:00,861 --> 00:36:03,822
He was in the centre
of a one-mile video blackout.

493
00:36:03,906 --> 00:36:06,784
Unless this is a coincidence,
which is doubtful,

494
00:36:06,867 --> 00:36:09,161
there's no way
this is straight B and E.

495
00:36:09,245 --> 00:36:12,081
Maybe, but Eisenberg
is on the crime desk,

496
00:36:12,164 --> 00:36:15,084
and you are a staff reporter
way past deadline.

497
00:36:17,461 --> 00:36:20,965
Don't make me regret
working for people in their 50s.

498
00:36:21,048 --> 00:36:22,383
40s.

499
00:36:24,051 --> 00:36:25,469
One week.

500
00:36:36,355 --> 00:36:38,816
Francie, sweetie,
you're overreacting.

501
00:36:38,899 --> 00:36:42,695
Charlie's cheating on me.
I have proof. I found something.

502
00:36:42,778 --> 00:36:46,991
It's a matchbook with some girl's
name and phone number written in it.

503
00:36:47,575 --> 00:36:50,119
Copy. We're five minutes out.

504
00:36:50,202 --> 00:36:54,248
- That could mean anything.
- It says, "I loved tonight. Rachel."

505
00:36:55,332 --> 00:36:58,460
- The matchbook is from a hotel.
- Fran.

506
00:36:58,544 --> 00:37:02,256
Don't assume the worst yet.
You won't know until you know.

507
00:37:02,339 --> 00:37:05,134
The truth isn't what it seems.
Bitte, nicht!

508
00:37:05,217 --> 00:37:08,679
- Where are you?
- With a client. I'll call you back.

509
00:37:08,762 --> 00:37:10,764
Clear to land the bird.

510
00:37:12,933 --> 00:37:16,395
Listen up. Per agreement
with the Directorate,

511
00:37:16,478 --> 00:37:18,856
we'll divide the stadium
down the middle.

512
00:37:18,939 --> 00:37:20,941
They get the west, we get the east.

513
00:37:21,025 --> 00:37:24,528
Alpha team, you're on rear overwatch,
in case they surprise us.

514
00:37:24,612 --> 00:37:27,489
Bravo and Charlie,
you're on countersnipers.

515
00:37:27,573 --> 00:37:29,491
The rules of engagement are,

516
00:37:29,575 --> 00:37:33,412
you're authorised to fire
only if our assets are fired upon.

517
00:37:34,496 --> 00:37:36,665
K- Directorate are taking position.

518
00:37:41,754 --> 00:37:45,341
Hold positions. We're waiting
for Bristow to go hot-mic.

519
00:38:08,614 --> 00:38:12,326
- Who am I talking to?
- Your invisible friend.

520
00:38:12,409 --> 00:38:14,537
Good. Where are you?

521
00:38:14,620 --> 00:38:19,250
Satellite relay station back in LA,
watching you from a 200-mile orbit.

522
00:38:19,875 --> 00:38:21,752
My guardian angel.

523
00:38:22,795 --> 00:38:25,381
I was gonna say the same thing
to you.

524
00:38:26,298 --> 00:38:29,009
- Thanks for the promotion.
- You're welcome.

525
00:38:29,093 --> 00:38:30,553
Heads up.

526
00:38:36,851 --> 00:38:39,186
- Team leader, we're hot.
- Copy that.

527
00:38:39,687 --> 00:38:41,063
She's coming.

528
00:38:42,815 --> 00:38:45,734
Have you two spoken,
about her mother?

529
00:38:47,319 --> 00:38:50,698
Yes. She asked me about her death.

530
00:38:50,781 --> 00:38:53,492
Did you tell her the truth?

531
00:39:54,303 --> 00:39:56,513
How's your Russian these days?

532
00:40:05,981 --> 00:40:07,942
I heard about your fiancé.

533
00:40:08,025 --> 00:40:10,444
Very sad.

534
00:40:10,528 --> 00:40:14,949
I thought it was a security execution
sanctioned by your employers.

535
00:40:17,159 --> 00:40:20,829
Maybe you said something
in your sleep you shouldn't have.

536
00:40:23,290 --> 00:40:26,585
But then, why would you be here
in service

537
00:40:26,669 --> 00:40:29,588
of the men
that killed your true love?

538
00:40:38,889 --> 00:40:42,059
- I take it you brought the key.
- I take it you brought the box.

539
00:40:42,142 --> 00:40:46,021
Once we see what's inside,
we go our separate ways.

540
00:41:22,057 --> 00:41:23,475
Oh, my God!



